      "message": "I think this method can be combined with the previous method, we might need to a flag to indicate it is create or update.\n\nlook at table of combinations\n\nCREATE\nOLD NEW   Accept\nN/A Blank True\nN/A New   True\nN/A Dupl. False\nN/A Batch False (should BOTH get rejected!)\n\nUPDATE\nOLD NEW   Accept\nN/A   Blank True\nSame  Same  True  *New Scenario\nOther New   False *New Scenario\nBlank New   True\nN/A   Dupl. False\nN/A   Batch False (should BOTH get rejected!)\n\nConclusion after review meeting: Extusingmethdos can be used, just update documentation and add test for update specific scenarios (indicated by *)",
